title: Joe Louis Walker - Ridin' High Live (2003) [FLAC]
description:
From Hightone's 'Heritage of the Blues' series this live album compiles the best of Joe Louis Walker's live at Slim's tracks recorded on November 9th and 10th, 1990. The album includes three previously unreleased tracks, 'Alligator', 'Personal Baby' & 'Prove Your Love'. 

Joe Louis Walker - Heritage Of The Blues - Ridin'High live
Label: Hightone Records - HCD8162
Format: CD, Album, Compilation, Reissue, Remastered
Country: US
Released: 2003
Recorded at Slim's, San Francisco, CA on November 9-10, 1990
Genre: Blues
Style: Modern Electric Blues

11. One Time Around (5:33)
